YouAre Theme Installation Instructions:


1. Unpack or unzip YouAre.
2. Log in to the WordPress Administration Dashboard. Go to Plugins menu and active plugins uploaded.
3. Upload the /youare folder to your /wp-content/themes directory.
4. Click 'Themes' sub-menu from 'Appearance' menu.
5. Activate the YouAre theme from the available list of themes to preview.
6. Click on the YouAre Options menu item, scroll to the bottom and click "Save".
7. To make an archive page: add new page with page template 'Archives'.
8. To make a tag cloud page: add new page with page template 'Tags'.